name: Hullmod installer
desc: A hull alteration is a special, consumeable hull modification, that can be installed through the "Additional Options" section at the top of the refit screen.

name: Artifact
desc: An ancient device that can be integrated in to the fleet and provide benefits for it. Only one can be active at a time. Integrating the first artifact opens the "Artifacts" intel tab in the "Personal" section, providing more information.
